//Molecule Link Button
.molecule-link-button {
  cursor: pointer;
  position: absolute !important;
  top: 3px;
  right: 165px;
  z-index: 999;
  min-width: 200px;
  width: 200px;
  border-radius: 5px;
  height: 25px;
  align-items: center;
  justify-content: space-evenly;
  display: flex;
  box-shadow: none !important;
  color: #4A71C2;
  background-color: #ffffff;

  .navigate-icon{
    content: url("data:image/svg+xml, %3Csvg width='10' height='10' viewBox='0 0 10 10' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M8.88889 8.88889H1.11111V1.11111H5V0H1.11111C0.494444 0 0 0.5 0 1.11111V8.88889C0 9.5 0.494444 10 1.11111 10H8.88889C9.5 10 10 9.5 10 8.88889V5H8.88889V8.88889ZM6.11111 0V1.11111H8.10556L2.64444 6.57222L3.42778 7.35556L8.88889 1.89444V3.88889H10V0H6.11111Z' fill='%234A71C2'/%3E%3C/svg%3E%0A");
  }

  .molecule-icon{
    content: url("data:image/svg+xml, %3Csvg width='82' height='18' viewBox='0 0 82 18' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Crect width='81.5625' height='18' fill='url(%23pattern0)'/%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cpattern id='pattern0' patternContentUnits='objectBoundingBox' width='1' height='1'%3E%3Cuse xlink:href='%23image0_43_1124' transform='scale(0.00137931 0.00625)'/%3E%3C/pattern%3E%3Cimage id='image0_43_1124' width='725' height='160' xlink:href='data:image/png;base64,'/%3E%3C/defs%3E%3C/svg%3E%0A");
  }

  .label{
    color: #4A71C2;
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 12px;
  }

  &:hover {
    color: #1D9FFF;
    background-color: #37414F !important;

    .navigate-icon{
      content: url("data:image/svg+xml, %3Csvg width='10' height='10' viewBox='0 0 10 10' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg'%3E%3Cpath d='M8.88889 8.88889H1.11111V1.11111H5V0H1.11111C0.494444 0 0 0.5 0 1.11111V8.88889C0 9.5 0.494444 10 1.11111 10H8.88889C9.5 10 10 9.5 10 8.88889V5H8.88889V8.88889ZM6.11111 0V1.11111H8.10556L2.64444 6.57222L3.42778 7.35556L8.88889 1.89444V3.88889H10V0H6.11111Z' fill='%231D9FFF'/%3E%3C/svg%3E%0A");
    }
  
    .molecule-icon{
      content: url("data:image/svg+xml, %3Csvg width='82' height='18' viewBox='0 0 82 18' fill='none' xmlns='http://www.w3.org/2000/svg' xmlns:xlink='http://www.w3.org/1999/xlink'%3E%3Crect width='81.5625' height='18' fill='url(%23pattern0)'/%3E%3Cdefs%3E%3Cpattern id='pattern0' patternContentUnits='objectBoundingBox' width='1' height='1'%3E%3Cuse xlink:href='%23image0_43_2246' transform='scale(0.00137931 0.00625)'/%3E%3C/pattern%3E%3Cimage id='image0_43_2246' width='725' height='160' xlink:href='data:image/png;base64,'/%3E%3C/defs%3E%3C/svg%3E%0A");
    }
  
    .label{
      color: #1D9FFF;
      font-weight: 500;
      font-size: 12px;
    }
  }
}
